metadata.name: WarpChecks Open Edition
metadata.description:
Checks-style art created by YoshiWins, using WVRPS #9579

First snapshot taken shortly after mint ends. Mint because you like the art, and everything else is gravy. Fair warning: Yoshi likes gravy, so there will be gravy, especially if you're a fellow WVRPS holder. But, even non-WVRPS holders will get a little gravy. Be careful cooking the gravy... you might burn it.

Not a WVRPS holder? No idea what WVRPS are? Wake up to the pioneer music NFT powered by generative AI artists who were around before AI was cool.

Original WVRPS NFT: https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0xcbc67ea382f8a006d46eeeb7255876beb7d7f14d/9579

Warpsound AI, the creators of WVRPS:  
https://www.warpsound.ai/
